# {{name}}

A Vibe app — **plain TypeScript**, typesafe by default. No custom file extensions.

- `agents/*.ts` — each default-exports an agent (auto-discovered).
- `tools/*.ts` — each default-exports a tool (auto-discovered).
- `vibe.config.ts` — app config via `defineConfig`.

```sh
bun install
bun run build        # optimized, tree-shaken, code-split serverless bundles
bun run check        # TypeScript type-check
```

Set `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` to run against the live model; without it, agents use a
deterministic fake provider so everything runs offline.
